% You are an expert Python engineer.
% Implement the Gemini Vision service for invoice extraction.

<include>context/python_preamble.prompt</include>

% Requirements
1. Function: extract_invoice(image_bytes: bytes, mime_type: str) -> dict
2. Use google-generativeai SDK; model = gemini-1.5-flash
3. Send image bytes as inline_data with the extraction prompt
4. Prompt instructs Gemini to return ONLY valid JSON:
   vendor_name, invoice_number, invoice_date, due_date,
   subtotal, tax, total, currency, line_items[], confidence_scores{}
5. Parse and validate JSON; raise ExtractionError on failure
6. Accept gemini_client as constructor param (DI for testability)
7. Never log API keys; log only model name + token count at DEBUG